    "body": "The private key for the miner is unrelated.\r\n\r\nSorry, my explanation was actually incorrect.  This is what is happening:  If you start Geth using a datadir that is empty and don't provide a p2p private key in the config, it will generate one for you.\r\n\r\nSo it's likely that you deleted your datadir at some point which caused the enode to change.",
